{"tid":2417120,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"有邊句座右銘你記到宜家","createTime":"2021-02-21T15:05:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T16:22:43.000Z","uid":109748,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd26135455f431b66f47645dba5041fd45394da","tid":2417120,"uid":109748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:05:25.000Z","msg":"呢個post唔係攞嚟扮有正能量心靈雞湯嘅，純粹想知大家做人有冇咩座右銘<br />\n<br />\n我先<br />\n話到口中留幾句   理從是處讓三分<br />\n提住自己禍從口出，冇把握嘅嘢唔識嘅嘢唔好講出口<br />\n同埋最緊要係後一句，就算自己啱晒，道理係自己到都讓吓人<br />\n唔好自己攞晒彩"},{"pid":"2274f321348b308f8c859bd06f7dc6b7d2dcf406","tid":2417120,"uid":212623,"like":11,"dislike":17,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:08:25.000Z","msg":"全部女人都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e250276047f3d3820346b56fc6a2a52261c00b6","tid":2417120,"uid":2781,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:09:02.000Z","msg":"毒撚最忌有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f18ee405d4e03a28a771dc1cebc68b8f305b3a","tid":2417120,"uid":254254,"like":63,"dislike":10,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"光<br />\n復<br />\n香<br />\n港<br />\n時<br />\n代<br />\n革<br />\n命<br />\n五<br />\n大<br />\n訴<br />\n求<br />\n缺<br />\n一<br />\n不<br />\n可"},{"pid":"0acc4b709605b4021ad1fb8851baab3ff9142677","tid":2417120,"uid":252972,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:11:15.000Z","msg":"做得狗預左皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"33fc99f6f40697c7ccb90a04c1cbcf6ca3a87a59","tid":2417120,"uid":252972,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:16:02.000Z","msg":"講返個正經先<br />\n就算走冤枉路都比原地踏步好"},{"pid":"d7861cd30b74b21ce9dc5896fa02f91c2420761d","tid":2417120,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T15:16:44.000Z","msg":"靚女唔痾屎"},{"pid":"27f2010feb19ae7f54d4858b228886fdb5de3219","tid":2417120,"uid":162539,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2